00:47:49,129 --> 00:47:51,629
記念、グッズ！
Anniversary goods!

585
00:47:53,129 --> 00:47:54,629
ワオ！
Wow!

586
00:47:55,129 --> 00:47:57,929
活動1周年記念グッズ！
1st Anniversary Commemorative Goods!

